# 🤝 Hissa Qo'shish (Contributing)

YusufAI loyihasiga qo'shgan hissangiz uchun rahmat! 🎉

---

## 📋 Qanday Hissa Qo'shish Mumkin?

### 1. 🐛 Bug Report
Xato topdingizmi? Issue oching:
- Xatoning tavsifi
- Qanday takrorlash mumkin
- Kutilgan natija
- Screenshot (agar kerak bo'lsa)

### 2. ✨ Feature Request
Yangi fikringiz bormi? Bizga ayting:
- Qanday xususiyat
- Nima uchun kerak
- Qanday ishlashi kerak

### 3. 💻 Code Contribution
Kod yozmoqchimisiz?

---

## 🚀 Development Setup

```bash
# 1. Fork qiling
# GitHub'da "Fork" tugmasini bosing

# 2. Clone qiling
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/YusufAI.git
cd YusufAI

# 3. Backend setup
cd backend
pip install -r requirements.txt
cp .env.example .env
# .env ga API keylarni qo'shing

# 4. Frontend test
cd ../frontend
# demo.html ni oching

# 5. Branch yarating
git checkout -b feature/amazing-feature

# 6. Kod yozing
# ...

# 7. Test qiling
python backend/app.py
# Frontend test

# 8. Commit
git add .
git commit -m "Add: amazing feature"

# 9. Push
git push origin feature/amazing-feature

# 10. Pull Request
# GitHub'da PR oching
```

---

## 📐 Code Style

### Python (Backend)
```python
# PEP 8 standard
# Funktsiyalar - snake_case
def get_user_data():
    pass

# Klasslar - PascalCase
class UserManager:
    pass

# Konstantalar - UPPERCASE
API_KEY = "..."

# Docstrings
def process_message(text):
    """Process incoming message.
    
    Args:
        text (str): User message
        
    Returns:
        str: AI response
    """
    pass
```

### JavaScript (Frontend)
```javascript
// camelCase
function sendMessage() {}

// Constants - UPPER_CASE
const API_URL = "...";

// Arrow functions
const getData = () => {};

// Comments
// Single line
/* Multi
   line */
```

### HTML/CSS
```html
<!-- Semantic HTML -->
<section class="chat-container">
  <div class="message user">...</div>
</section>
```

```css
/* BEM notation */
.chat-container {}
.chat-container__message {}
.chat-container__message--user {}
```

---

## ✅ Pull Request Checklist

Pull Request ochishdan oldin:

- [ ] Kod ishlayapti (local test)
- [ ] Xatolik yo'q (no errors)
- [ ] Code style to'g'ri
- [ ] Comments qo'shilgan
- [ ] README yangilangan (kerak bo'lsa)
- [ ] Branch nomi to'g'ri (`feature/`, `fix/`, `docs/`)
- [ ] Commit message aniq

---

## 📝 Commit Message Format

```
Type: Brief description

Longer description (optional)

Fixes #123
```

**Types:**
- `Add:` Yangi xususiyat
- `Fix:` Bug fix
- `Update:` Mavjud xususiyatni yangilash
- `Remove:` O'chirish
- `Docs:` Documentation
- `Style:` Code formatting
- `Refactor:` Code refactoring
- `Test:` Testlar
- `Chore:` Maintenance

**Misol:**
```
Add: Voice input feature

Added Web Speech API integration for voice input.
Users can now speak instead of typing.

Fixes #42
```

---

## 🧪 Testing

```bash
# Backend test
python -m pytest backend/tests/

# Manual test
python backend/app.py
# Browser'da test qiling
```

