## 📖 Documentation

Yangi feature qo'shsangiz:
- README.md ni yangilang
- docs/ papkasiga qo'shing
- Code comments yozing
- API docs yangilang

---

## 🎯 Priority Issues

Agar qayerdan boshlashni bilmasangiz:
- `good first issue` label
- `help wanted` label
- `priority: high` label

